{"tid":1966038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京讚譚德塞：客觀、科學、公正","createTime":"2020-04-10T01:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T02:11:12.000Z","uid":47496,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"40179617cab117104c9fada9de6dc1307fd4aa4e","tid":1966038,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:35:28.000Z","msg":"〔記者鍾麗華／綜合報導〕對於世衛組織秘書長譚德塞稱台灣對他種族歧視和人身攻擊，中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨天在例行記者會上未正面回答，但他稱，中國一如既往地堅定支援世衛組織工作和在全球抗疫合作中的領導作用，還讚揚世衛組織在譚德塞的領導下，為推動國際抗疫合作發揮重要作用。<br />\n<br />\n被問到「台灣這三個月來對譚德塞發動人身攻擊」，趙立堅僅表示，「台灣島內部分人『以疫謀獨』的企圖，不會得逞。」<br />\n<br />\n對於世衛近來迭遭美國總統川普批評，趙立堅稱，新冠肺炎疫情發生以來，「世衛組織在譚德塞領導下，積極履行自身職責，秉持客觀、科學、公正的立場，為協助各國應對疫情、推動國際抗疫合作發揮了重要作用，得到國際社會普遍認可與高度讚揚」。<br />\n<br />\n中國國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮則聲稱，「民進黨當局以疫謀獨不擇手段，惡毒攻擊世衛組織及其負責人，縱容綠營網軍肆意散佈種族歧視言論。」她要民進黨當局立即停止政治操弄，藉疫情破壞一中原則和謀求加入世衛圖謀是不會得逞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1364896?_gl=1*1tuzau7*_ga*RTVUVHdGaTVGUl9fbXZuVGpNTnFQc1dLMXlUTFdnMm94XzJoM1hUVHN0UjhScURUclRNX2tXX21ySFBleDd6UA..\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1364896%3F_gl%3D1%2A1tuzau7%2A_ga%2ARTVUVHdGaTVGUl9fbXZuVGpNTnFQc1dLMXlUTFdnMm94XzJoM1hUVHN0UjhScURUclRNX2tXX21ySFBleDd6UA..&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6w2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=5a1f57b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1364896%3F_gl%3D1%2A1tuzau7%2A_ga%2ARTVUVHdGaTVGUl9fbXZuVGpNTnFQc1dLMXlUTFdnMm94XzJoM1hUVHN0UjhScURUclRNX2tXX21ySFBleDd6UA..&h=c6eb26dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1364896?_gl=1*1tuzau7*_ga*RTVUVHdGaTVGUl9fbXZuVGpNTnFQc1dLMXlUTFdnMm94XzJoM1hUVHN0UjhScURUclRNX2tXX21ySFBleDd6UA..</a>"},{"pid":"08d53f3d787071fafd0b1f248b6c431ac767d7fb","tid":1966038,"uid":324712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:36:55.000Z","msg":"黑人、撚大、無腦"},{"pid":"e77e88e315586a7efae2f06395ac0061ad0f0cb9","tid":1966038,"uid":47496,"like":1,"dislike":0